typeProperties.script:
source(output(
		ProductID as integer,
		Name as string,
		ProductNumber as string,
		Color as string,
		StandardCost as decimal(19,4),
		ListPrice as decimal(19,4),
		Size as string,
		Weight as decimal(8,2),
		ProductCategoryID as integer,
		ProductModelID as integer,
		SellStartDate as timestamp,
		SellEndDate as timestamp,
		DiscontinuedDate as timestamp,
		ThumbnailPhotoFileName as string,
		rowguid as string,
		ModifiedDate as timestamp
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	format: 'table') ~> source1
source(output(
		ProductID as integer,
		Name as string,
		ProductNumber as string,
		Color as string,
		StandardCost as decimal(19,4),
		ListPrice as decimal(19,4),
		Size as string,
		Weight as decimal(8,2),
		ProductCategoryID as integer,
		ProductModelID as integer,
		SellStartDate as timestamp,
		SellEndDate as timestamp,
		DiscontinuedDate as timestamp,
		ThumbnailPhotoFileName as string,
		rowguid as string,
		ModifiedDate as timestamp
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	format: 'table') ~> source2
SurrogateKey1 window(over(category),
	asc(sk, true),
	startRowOffset: -1L,
	endRowOffset: 0L,
	sk2 = first(sk)) ~> Window
source1 derive(category = 'prods') ~> DerivedColumn1
DerivedColumn1 keyGenerate(output(sk as long),
	startAt: 1L) ~> SurrogateKey1
source2 derive(Color = iif(Color == 'Silver',toString(null()),Color),
		dummy = 1) ~> DerivedColumn2
SurrogateKey2 window(over(dummy),
	asc(lookup_sk, true),
	value_sk = iifNull(last(Color),first(Color),last(Color))) ~> Window1
DerivedColumn2 keyGenerate(output(lookup_sk as long),
	startAt: 1L) ~> SurrogateKey2
Window1 sink(mapColumn(
		ProductID,
		Color,
		lookup_sk,
		value_sk
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true,
	keys:['ProductID'],
	store: 'cache',
	format: 'inline',
	saveOrder: 1) ~> sink1
